desc: TOOKE clothing , pronounced “took” , stands for ‘Take Out Obstacles Keep Elevating & Everything you do, do it with love 💙’. Tooke clothing originating in Venice, Ca, makes productive wear. Clothing to keep you motivated and inspired. Clothes that makes you look good. If you can see it you can achieve it 👀 TOOKE
